  "article_text": "Welcome to the Star Atlas weekly recap from the Intergalactic Herald. Below is what happened with Star Atlas this past week.\nWe are looking for guests to be on our podcast. The podcast is a discussion of the past week’s news about Star Atlas. If you are interested in being on the podcast, please contact us.\nWe are launching a Star Atlas merch store. Please check it out at Intergalactic Gear.\nWe are creating a “non-guild” guild. If you are interested in learning more, please go to Intergalactic Coalition.\nStar Atlas Lets Build A Fleet!!\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video building his Star Atlas fleet.\nStar Atlas Chatter #11 – SAGE Labs & Does SIZE Matter?\nRahMega posted a video recapping the past week of Star Atlas news.\nMetaverse Nomads #109 Star Atlas\nMetaVerse Nomads posted a video replay of their Star Atlas livestream.\nWEEKLY STAR ATLAS NEWSLETTER #94\nAephia published their weekly Star Atlas newsletter.\nStar Atlas – 2023 Development Sneak Peek\nStar Atlas posted a video looking at ongoing game development.\n10 | WHAT THE @#$% HAPPENED TO MY STAR ATLAS EARNINGS???\nPathfinder posted a video looking at Star Atlas earnings.\nStar Atas Amazing Video & Sage Labs Spreadsheets\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video about the latest Star Atlas news.\nSTAR ATLAS #195 FORM YOUR FLEETS NOW!\nMetaVerse Explorer posted a video of Star Atlas updates.\nStar Atlas – Preparing for SAGE Labs (Zero to Hero)\nAtlas Theory posted a video in his Zero to Hero series.\nAtlas Brew #77\nThe Hologram News Network posted a video replay of the latest Atlas Brew.\nThe Atlas Brew #77\nStar Atlas TV posted a video replay of the latest Atlas Brew.\nStar Atlas Recap August 31 2023\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video recapping the latest Star Atlas news.",
